		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Particle swarm optimization</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Particle swarm optimization (PSO)</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Swarm_intelligence" title="Swarm intelligence">swarm intelligence</a> based <a href="/wiki/Algorithm" title="Algorithm">algorithm</a> to find a solution to an optimization problem in a <a href="/wiki/Search_space" title="Search space">search space</a>, or model and predict social behavior in the presence of objectives.</p>
